spec_data.Name: NetworkManager-glib
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the libraries that make it easier to use some
NetworkManager functionality from applications that use glib.  This is
the older NetworkManager API. See also NetworkManager-libnm.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 17 Nov 2017 05:22:14 PM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Libraries for adding NetworkManager support to applications (old API).
